Package uk.ac.ed.inf.DronePath

Class PathNode

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.ed.inf.DronePath.PathNode
public class PathNode extends Object
PathNode helps represent LngLat details like a graphical node. This helps link coordinates and store heuristic values for PathGenerator.AStarSearch(NoFlyZone[], CentralArea, PathNode, PathNode).
